《'''轻轻摇晃'''》({{lang-en|Lilting}}）是一部2014年英国剧情片，由短片作品《春》入选2011年柏林电影节和[[圣丹斯电影节|圣丹斯电影节]]的柬埔寨出生的华裔[[许泰丰|许泰丰]]（Hong Khaou）导演<ref>{{cite web|url=http://microwave.filmlondon.org.uk/get_inspired/lilting/cast_and_crew/|title=Microwave – Get Inspired – Lilting – Cast and Crew – Crew – Writer/Director – Hong Khaou|publisher=|access-date=2015-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130521171118/http://microwave.filmlondon.org.uk/get_inspired/lilting/cast_and_crew/|archive-date=2013-05-21|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，多米尼克·布坎南制片<ref>{{cite web|url=http://microwave.filmlondon.org.uk/get_inspired/lilting/cast_and_crew/crew/producer_dominic_buchanan|title=Microwave – Get Inspired – Lilting – Cast and Crew – Crew – Producer – Dominic Buchanan|publisher=|access-date=2015-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140808045511/http://microwave.filmlondon.org.uk/get_inspired/lilting/cast_and_crew/crew/producer_dominic_buchanan|archive-date=2014-08-08|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。影片于2014年1月16日圣丹斯电影节首日全球首映<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sundance.org/festival/release/2014-festival-us-world-and-next-films-announced/|title=Sundance Institute Announces Films in U.S. and World Competitions, NEXT  for 2014 Sundance Film Festival – Sundance Film Festival|publisher=|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131205162021/http://www.sundance.org/festival/release/2014-festival-us-world-and-next-films-announced/|archivedate=2013-12-05}}</ref>，赢得世界电影戏剧大赛摄影奖<ref>{{cite web|title=Sundance: 'Whiplash' & 'Rich Hill' Win Grand Jury Awards; Dramatic Directing Goes To Cutter Hodierne For 'Fishing Without Nets'|url=http://www.deadline.com/2014/01/sundance-film-festival-winners-2014-awards-list/|accessdate=January 26, 2014|archive-date=2014-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140612062005/http://www.deadline.com/2014/01/sundance-film-festival-winners-2014-awards-list/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title='Whiplash' Owns the 2014 Sundance Film Festival Awards Netting Two Top Prizes|url=http://www.indiewire.com/article/the-2014-sundance-film-festival-winners-as-they-come-in|accessdate=January 26, 2014|archive-date=2016-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160507014337/http://www.indiewire.com/article/the-2014-sundance-film-festival-winners-as-they-come-in|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年8月8日影片于英国上映<ref>{{cite web|title=Lilting UK release date|url=http://www.filmdates.co.uk/films/6746-lilting/|accessdate=August 18, 2014|archive-date=2016-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160325072247/http://www.filmdates.co.uk/films/6746-lilting/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Lilting BBC UK|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/bbcfilms/film/lilting|accessdate=August 18, 2014|archive-date=2014-08-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140814051730/http://www.bbc.co.uk/bbcfilms/film/lilting|dead-url=no}}</ref>，2014年9月26日于美国上映<ref>{{cite web|title=Lilting|url=https://www.yahoo.com/movies/film/lilting|accessdate=August 18, 2014|archive-date=2016-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160420094331/https://www.yahoo.com/movies/film/lilting|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 剧情 ==
在儿子突然去世后，一位母亲试图去了解儿子的过去。儿子男友的出现打乱了她的生活。尽管没有共同的语言，他们试图去战胜相同的痛苦。<ref name="Cooper">{{cite web | url = https://www.screendaily.com/news/uk-ireland/tony-grisonis-kingsland-amongst-new-microwave-projects/5042214.article | title = Tony Grisoni's Kingsland amongst new Microwave projects | author = Cooper, Sarah | language = en | publisher = Screen Daily | date = 2012-05-19 | accessdate = 2020-12-14 | archive-date = 2018-10-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181029112224/https://www.screendaily.com/news/uk-ireland/tony-grisonis-kingsland-amongst-new-microwave-projects/5042214.article | dead-url = no }}</ref>

