== 制作 ==
剧本原题《轻快的过往》（Lilting the Past），在2011年最佳未制作英国电影剧本榜单Brit List中夺得第三名<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118045861|title='Call Up' tops Brit List|work=Variety|access-date=2015-02-11|archive-date=2012-03-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120315060548/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118045861|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2012年，影片是Microwave三部开绿灯的作品中的一部<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118054312?refCatId=1061|title=Microwave heats up three pics|work=Variety}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://unitedagents.co.uk/node/5328|title=Hong Khaou's LILTING announced among new Microwave projects – United Agents|publisher=|access-date=2015-02-11|archive-date=2016-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160421233238/http://unitedagents.co.uk/node/5328|dead-url=no}}</ref>。剧组随后公布了三名主演<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.chinatownartsspace.com/files/casting_for_lilting.pdf |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-11-29  |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121113150536/http://www.chinatownartsspace.com/files/casting_for_lilting.pdf |archivedate=2012-11-13 }}</ref>，随后由[[郑佩佩|郑佩佩]]和[[Andrew_Leung|Andrew Leung]]填补。

2012年11月开始摄制。导演许泰丰称电影受到了[[王家卫|王家卫]]《[[花样年华|花样年华]]》的视觉启发<ref>{{cite web|url=http://microwave.filmlondon.org.uk/get_inspired/lilting/directors_vision/|title=Microwave – Get Inspired – Lilting – Directors Vision|publisher=|access-date=2015-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130521212806/http://microwave.filmlondon.org.uk/get_inspired/lilting/directors_vision/|archive-date=2013-05-21|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。制片过程中，Microwave安排迈克尔·温特伯顿辅导编剧兼导演许泰丰，布坎南由《[[伦敦到布莱顿|伦敦到布莱顿]]》、《[[污垢|污垢]]》和《[[献给爱妻的歌|献给爱妻的歌]]》制片人[[肯·马歇尔|肯·马歇尔]]执导<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.screendaily.com/news/production/microwaves-lilting-starring-ben-whishaw-underway-in-london/5049666.article?blocktitle=Latest-news&contentID=1846|title=Microwave's Lilting, starring Ben Whishaw, underway in London|publisher=|access-date=2015-02-11|archive-date=2019-12-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191207093005/https://www.screendaily.com/news/production/microwaves-lilting-starring-ben-whishaw-underway-in-london/5049666.article?blocktitle=Latest-news&contentID=1846|dead-url=no}}</ref>。预算跟所有Microwave导演一样是12万英镑。影片是Microwave计划中的第一部双语电影<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.standard.co.uk/news/celebritynews/ben-whishaw-goes-from-skyfall-q-to-budget-film-8399271.html|title=Ben Whishaw goes from Skyfall Q to budget film|work=The Evening Standard|access-date=2015-02-11|archive-date=2019-12-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191209011636/https://www.standard.co.uk/news/celebritynews/ben-whishaw-goes-from-skyfall-q-to-budget-film-8399271.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 评价 ==
《轻轻摇晃》获得评论家的积极评价。影评聚合网站[[烂番茄|烂番茄]]基于24条积极评价，打出96%的“新鲜度”，评级得分6.9（满分10分）<ref>{{cite web|title=Lilting (2014)|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/lilting/|work=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|publisher=Flixster|accessdate=August 19, 2014|archive-date=2020-10-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201004103604/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/lilting|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
